    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-8094-885f-cc21382e9058",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Descriptive modelling is under-explored in comparison to the creation of models that predict performance. Authors draw from pattern mining and NLP to extract the most frequent learning strategies from a blended course.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1914750c-f3ba-8094-885f-cc21382e9058",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
