    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-80c6-bc73-cc41c99106a1",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Results show that, depending on the assessments the student is preparing for, the patterns of interaction with the LMS differ considerably. The results show that the hybrid NLP approach may generate decent descriptions of student behavior and be used to predict performance. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
